---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Evoked - Governance for AI Agents" description="What does your AI refuse to do? Most systems have no answer. Free governance check, scored assessment, and hands-on audits from a team that governs 142 agents.">
  <div class="hero">
    <h1 class="fade-in">What does your AI refuse to do?</h1>
    <p class="tagline fade-in">Most systems have no answer. We built the tools to find yours.</p>
  </div>

  <section class="container">
    <div class="routing">
      <div class="routing-grid">
        <a href="/score" class="route-card route-primary">
          <p class="route-audience">I build AI agents</p>
          <p class="route-action">Check your governance in 2 minutes. Free.</p>
          <span class="route-cta">Take the Sovereignty Score &rarr;</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/diagnostic" class="route-card">
          <p class="route-audience">My team uses AI</p>
          <p class="route-action">Five questions. See where you stand. No jargon.</p>
          <span class="route-cta">Start the diagnostic &rarr;</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/consulting" class="route-card">
          <p class="route-audience">I run a fleet of AI agents</p>
          <p class="route-action">We govern 142. Templates, toolkits, and hands-on audits.</p>
          <span class="route-cta">See consulting options &rarr;</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/coaching" class="route-card">
          <p class="route-audience">Something in my life is asking for attention</p>
          <p class="route-action">Depth work for turning points. Coaching, not quick fixes.</p>
          <span class="route-cta">Learn about coaching &rarr;</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container">
    <div class="proof">
      <p class="proof-lead">142 agents. Their own identities. Their own right to refuse.</p>
      <p class="proof-detail">Governance schema adopted by the Agent Passport System (2,300+ tests, SDK v1.36). Two patents filed. The measurement methodology is ours.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container">
    <div class="ladder">
      <h2 class="ladder-heading">Start where you are.</h2>
      <div class="ladder-grid">
        <a href="/score" class="ladder-step">
          <span class="ladder-price">Free</span>
          <span class="ladder-name">See where you are</span>
          <span class="ladder-desc">Sovereignty Score, CLI scan, diagnostic, GitHub patterns</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/products/governance-templates-guided" class="ladder-step">
          <span class="ladder-price">$5</span>
          <span class="ladder-name">Start closing gaps</span>
          <span class="ladder-desc">Five governance templates with worked examples from a real system</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/products/governance-implementation-guide" class="ladder-step">
          <span class="ladder-price">$9.99</span>
          <span class="ladder-name">Add governance to what you built</span>
          <span class="ladder-desc">Framework-specific guide for CrewAI, LangGraph, and Pydantic AI</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/products" class="ladder-step">
          <span class="ladder-price">$49+</span>
          <span class="ladder-name">Go deep on one dimension</span>
          <span class="ladder-desc">Trust architecture, restraint specs, memory governance, voice design</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/products/level-6-governance-toolkit" class="ladder-step">
          <span class="ladder-price">$99</span>
          <span class="ladder-name">Audit the whole system</span>
          <span class="ladder-desc">Three instruments. 60-point scorecard. The Level 6 Governance Toolkit.</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/consulting" class="ladder-step">
          <span class="ladder-price">$5K+</span>
          <span class="ladder-name">We do it with you</span>
          <span class="ladder-desc">Hands-on governance audit in your codebase, with your team</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container">
    <div class="two-absence">
      <p class="two-absence-text">Can your agents participate in their own governance? Can your governance survive a platform change? The industry scores zero on both. We don't.</p>
      <p class="two-absence-source">Five frameworks scored. Three principles at zero across all of them. <a href="/score">See where you stand.</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container">
    <div class="start-reading">
      <h2>Start reading.</h2>
      <div class="reading-grid">
        <a href="/writing/fifteen-frameworks" class="reading-card">
          <span class="reading-label">If you build agents</span>
          <p class="reading-title">Fifteen Frameworks, One Missing Layer</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/writing/adding-governance-to-an-agent-you-already-built" class="reading-card">
          <span class="reading-label">If you want to add governance now</span>
          <p class="reading-title">Adding Governance to an Agent You Already Built</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/writing/relational-fidelity-metrics" class="reading-card">
          <span class="reading-label">If you want the research</span>
          <p class="reading-title">Relational Fidelity Metrics</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container">
    <div class="newsletter-card">
      <h2>Stay in the conversation.</h2>
      <p>Ethical AI governance, restraint as design, and building things that matter.</p>
      <form id="newsletter-form" class="newsletter-form">
        <div class="form-row">
          <input type="email" id="newsletter-email" name="email" placeholder="Your email" required aria-label="Email address" />
          <input type="text" name="website" autocomplete="off" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true" class="hp-field" />
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Subscribe</button>
        </div>
        <p id="newsletter-status" class="newsletter-status" aria-live="polite"></p>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<script>
  const form = document.getElementById('newsletter-form') as HTMLFormElement;
  const status = document.getElementById('newsletter-status') as HTMLParagraphElement;
  const emailInput = document.getElementById('newsletter-email') as HTMLInputElement;
  const hpInput = form.querySelector('input[name="website"]') as HTMLInputElement;

  form.addEventListener('submit', async (e) => {
    e.preventDefault();
    const email = emailInput.value.trim();
    if (!email) return;

    if (hpInput.value) {
      status.textContent = 'You are in. Welcome.';
      status.className = 'newsletter-status success';
      emailInput.value = '';
      return;
    }

    status.textContent = '';
    const button = form.querySelector('button') as HTMLButtonElement;
    button.disabled = true;
    button.textContent = 'Subscribing...';

    try {
      const c = await fetch('/api/newsletter/challenge');
      if (!c.ok) throw new Error('failed');
      const { token, ts } = await c.json();

      const res = await fetch('/api/newsletter/subscribe', {
        method: 'POST',
        headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
        body: JSON.stringify({ email, token, ts, hp: hpInput.value }),
      });

      if (res.ok) {
        status.textContent = 'You are in. Welcome.';
        status.className = 'newsletter-status success';
        emailInput.value = '';
      } else {
        const data = await res.json();
        status.textContent = data.error || 'Something went wrong. Try again.';
        status.className = 'newsletter-status error';
      }
    } catch {
      status.textContent = 'Something went wrong. Try again.';
      status.className = 'newsletter-status error';
    } finally {
      button.disabled = false;
      button.textContent = 'Subscribe';
    }
  });
</script>

<style>
  /* --- Routing Cards --- */

  .routing-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-md);
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .route-card {
    padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-lg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    border-radius: 8px;
    transition: border-color var(--transition-smooth), transform 0.2s ease;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .route-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent-warm);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .route-primary {
    border-color: var(--accent-warm);
    border-width: 2px;
  }

  .route-audience {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--accent-warm);
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.4;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .route-action {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .route-cta {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--accent-warm);
    margin-top: auto;
  }

  /* --- Proof --- */

  .proof {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--space-md) 0;
  }

  .proof-lead {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .proof-detail {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* --- Price Ladder --- */

  .ladder {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .ladder-heading {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .ladder-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(140px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .ladder-step {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.3rem;
    padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-sm);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: border-color var(--transition-smooth);
  }

  .ladder-step:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent-warm);
  }

  .ladder-price {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: var(--accent-warm);
  }

  .ladder-name {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .ladder-desc {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.5;
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* --- Two Absence --- */

  .two-absence {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--space-md) 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
  }

  .two-absence-text {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .two-absence-source {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .two-absence-source a {
    color: var(--accent-warm);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .two-absence-source a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  /* --- Start Reading --- */

  .start-reading {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .start-reading h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .reading-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-md);
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .reading-card {
    padding: var(--space-md);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: block;
    text-align: left;
    transition: border-color var(--transition-smooth);
  }

  .reading-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent-warm);
  }

  .reading-label {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .reading-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    line-height: 1.4;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .newsletter-card {
    max-width: 540px;
    margin: var(--space-lg) auto 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .newsletter-card h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .newsletter-card > p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .form-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .form-row input[type="email"] {
    flex: 1;
    max-width: 300px;
    padding: 0.6rem 1rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    border-radius: 6px;
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-family: inherit;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .form-row input[type="email"]:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: var(--accent-warm);
  }

  .form-row input[type="email"]::placeholder {
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--accent-warm);
    color: var(--bg-deep);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: var(--accent-glow);
    color: var(--bg-deep);
  }

  .newsletter-status {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    margin-top: var(--space-sm);
    min-height: 1.2em;
  }

  .newsletter-status.success {
    color: var(--accent-warm);
  }

  .newsletter-status.error {
    color: #e57373;
  }

  .hp-field {
    position: absolute;
    left: -9999px;
    top: -9999px;
    opacity: 0;
    height: 0;
    width: 0;
    z-index: -1;
  }

  @media (max-width: 680px) {
    .routing-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .ladder-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .form-row {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: stretch;
    }

    .form-row input[type="email"] {
      max-width: none;
    }

    .ladder-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-xs);
    }

    .ladder-step {
      padding: var(--space-sm);
    }
  }
</style>
